para_trans: Government Order No: Narrow 1325 / Q. No.11 / Pr.
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,

As per Section 4 (4) and 4 (5) of the Maharashtra Regulation of Transfer of Government Employees and Prevention of Delay in discharge of Government Duties Act, 2005, inter-departmental transfers are being made of officers of the rank of Deputy Secretary in the following Ministries and their posting is being done in the Department indicated in column-4 in front of their name.
These orders shall come into force with immediate effect.
3. General Administration Department, Government Circular No. As mentioned in the 25.08.2022, it is mandatory for the officers concerned to provide a transfer of charge certificate on discharge.
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
